title: Sibling Watchery - Drag Race All Stars Season 7 - Episode 9
description:
Bob and Monét review Drag Race All Stars Season 7 Episode 9 as the queens try to break the internet by creating an original dance video challenge. On the runway, category is: What Lies Beneath. Ben Platt lends his voice to the judges’ panel..
